config.script:
from java.lang import Class
	clazz = Class.forName('com.sepasoft.production.common.model.changelog.ChangeLogFilterFactory', False, system.mes.object.filter.createFilter().class.getClassLoader())
	filterFactory = clazz.getDeclaredMethod('select').invoke(None)
	
	recipeUUID = self.getSibling("mesObjectSelector").props.selectedMESObject.mesObjectUUID
	recLink = system.mes.getMESObjectLink('BatchMasterRecipe', recipeUUID)
	
	recObjList = system.mes.batch.recipe.loadRecipe(recLink)
	uuidList = []
	for obj in recObjList:
		uuidList.append(str(obj.getUUID()))
	
	filterFactory.byObjectUUID(uuidList)
	results = filterFactory.fetch()
	tableData = []
	for item in results:
		if str(item.getChangeEventType()) == 'COMPLEX_PROP_ADD':
			continue
		if item.getOldValue() == None or item.getOldValue() == '' or item.getOldValue() == 'null':
			continue
		path = item.getPath()
		tableData.append({
			'Name': item.getMESObjectName(),
			'Path': path[path.rfind('.') + 1:],
			'Old Value': item.getOldValue(),
			'New Value': item.getNewValue(),
			'Change Type': item.getChangeEventType(),
			'Time': item.getVersionTimeStamp().toString(),
			'By': item.getChangedByPersonName(),
			'Note': item.getChangeNote()
		})
	self.getSibling("Table").props.data = tableData
